{"tid":1879920,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱俾男朋友屌到跪咗喺度喊>·<","createTime":"2020-02-14T13:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T03:07:40.000Z","uid":150100,"like":207,"dislike":358,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"440fbd36b4d6cb5e76d5befb563d113f298af08b","tid":1879920,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日情人節就梗係做情人做嘅野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁今次其實係我嘅第一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇諗過原來會咁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者可能係佢嗰度比較大啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢每抽插一下我就痛到嗌三下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做咗幾分鐘我就頂唔順開始眼濕濕求佢停一停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢就開始痴咗線咁喺度屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一路大嗌停你老母咩臭雞<br />\n一路大大力咁抽插<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢突然間大嗌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後大大力一野插落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大力都算<br />\n仲要插錯窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n插咗落我個屎眼度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我即刻痛到跪咗度喊到收唔到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢仲屌鳩我話我唔識配合佢<br />\n搞到佢插錯窿，整污糟佢碌炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後仲係咁屌我話我喊乜鳩乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後見我喊到窒息咁先收口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係之後全日都唔理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚都冇食就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走嗰陣連bye bye都冇講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飛咗佢啦，痴線㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />忍佢，男人有啲脾氣好正常"},{"pid":"ca250c6ffd5f15786f5d992c582dd03029ccef1c","tid":1879920,"uid":276783,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:17:05.000Z","msg":"飛咗佢啦，痴線㗎"},{"pid":"26986fec072cbc421238ac865de4f53b5c53a2fc","tid":1879920,"uid":150100,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPSKefp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPSKefp.png&h=5922d2ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16a350233db49ef9476fdec17a87aabf66c895d3","tid":1879920,"uid":138138,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjTENA6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjTENA6.png&h=b072ea4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe6b26939f34de69773da8737e0d811921f4b51e","tid":1879920,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a350233db49ef9476fdec17a87aabf66c895d3","tid":1879920,"uid":138138,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjTENA6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjTENA6.png&h=b072ea4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6bbac5b4f1491818695f906d4bc00a46dd31e4","tid":1879920,"uid":84133,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T13:22:42.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"26144014042b43f5dc549aaea5c940e106c5c667","tid":1879920,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike"